    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a champ. It\u2019s in great shape and has plenty of life left in it\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable set of wheels without the brand-new price tag. It's super clean, runs smoothly, and I've really enjoyed my time with it. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
