      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained over the years. This is the perfect find if you're looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks fantastic on the road. It runs like a charm and is totally ready for its next big adventure with a new owner! Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love for you to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
