      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit has undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and recent valve clearance adjustments to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The drivetrain consists of a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a functional M-variable limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to mitigate floor fatigue, a common failure point in this chassis. Suspension kinematics are preserved through fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing the tactile feedback expected of this platform. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including cooling system components and rod bearing health\u2014are documented and robust. A true driver\u2019s specification for the discerning enthusiast.",
